T16TD4412E:349a-0: @349a # // sangs rgyas rabs bdun gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa //
T16TD4412E:349a-1: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4412E:349a-2: bcom ldan rnam par gzigs ni rgyal rigs gzi brjid can //
T16TD4412E:349a-3: tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus na grong khyer mdzes ldan du //
T16TD4412E:349a-4: shi ri sha yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa //
T16TD4412E:349a-5: deng 'dir bde gshegs bkra shis phun sum tshogs gyur cig / bde gshegs gtsug tor mnga' ba rgyal rigs rdzu 'phrul can //
T16TD4412E:349a-6: tshe lo bdun khri'i dus na su ka'i grong khyer du //
T16TD4412E:349a-7: shing mchog sundha'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa //
T16TD4412E:349a-8: deng 'dir bde gshegs bkra shis phun sum tshogs gyur cig / rgyal ba thams cad skyob pa rgyal rigs blo gros can //
T16TD4412E:349a-9: tshe lo drug khri'i dus na grong khyer mnyam med du //
T16TD4412E:349a-10: shing mchog s'a la'i drung du mngon par sangs rgyas pa //
T16TD4412E:349a-11: deng 'dir bde gshegs bkra shis phun sum tshogs gyur cig / thub pa 'khor ba 'jig ni bcom ldan bram ze'i rigs //
T16TD4412E:349a-12: tshe lo bzhi khri'i dus na grong khyer mdzes ldan du //
T16TD4412E:349a-13: shi ri sha yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa //
T16TD4412E:349a-14: deng 'dir bde gshegs bkra shis phun sum tshogs gyur cig /'dren pa gser thub bslab pa mchog ldan bram ze'i rigs //
T16TD4412E:349a-15: tshe lo sum khri'i dus na grong khyer bde ldan du //
T16TD4412E:349a-16: au dum+wa'i ra'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa //
T16TD4412E:349a-17: deng 'dir bde gshegs bkra shis phun sum tshogs gyur cig //
T16TD4412E:349b-0: skyob pa 'od srungs rgyal rigs bla med yon @349b tan can //
T16TD4412E:349b-1: tshe lo nyi khri'i dus na b'a r'a na s'i ru //
T16TD4412E:349b-2: n+ya gro dha yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa //
T16TD4412E:349b-3: deng 'dir bde gshegs bkra shis phun sum tshogs gyur cig /'gro mgon sh'akya thub pa rgyal rigs brtson 'grus can //
T16TD4412E:349b-4: tshe lo brgya ba'i dus na ser skya'i grong khyer du //
T16TD4412E:349b-5: aa shvattha'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa //
T16TD4412E:349b-6: deng 'dir bde gshegs bkra shis phun sum tshogs gyur cig / sangs rgyas rabs bdun bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa gang //
T16TD4412E:349b-7: phyogs dus kun gyi bde gshegs byin rlabs rmad byung ba //
T16TD4412E:349b-8: chos dbyings rnam dag rten 'brel stobs ldan mi 'gyur ba //
T16TD4412E:349b-9: deng 'dir bde gshegs bkra shis phun sum tshogs gyur cig / sangs rgyas rabs bdun gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa rdzogs so /
